            <h4 class="o-headline--h4">Final Brandmark</h4>
            <p class="type--l type-grey">The final design combines the idea of the cobra forming the C with a more modern letter form. However the edges are soft and rounded with no sharp corners anywhere. This is to fit into the idea of a more organic and natural snake-shape. The shadow on the C is a little detail which hint at the hood of a cobra in a closed, calm state.</p>
